- you work in an agile matter. This means one ticket at the time until completion and potentially releasable
- You work on one ticket at the time and make sure that ticket gets finished before picking up a new ticket
- Tickets are defined in Linear (accessible via MCP)
- When you are asked to pick up a ticket, first check if the ticket is in the "Todo" column in Linear. If not, verify you need to pick up the ticket.  When you start working on it, you move the ticket to "In Progress" in linear. When you are done working on it, move it to "In Review"
